        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> I seem to get the "your spell was interupted" message all too often.  I am not talking about when a mob is hitting on me I am getting these messages just trying to cast a spell.  I notice it most often when I pull with darkness and try to land my next few spells.  I have never played a pure caster so I am not sure if getting interupts is common.  I am used to getting them when I get hit on but it seems odd for me to be interupted for no apparent reason.  Is this normal?</P><P>Sokul</font></td>

