        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         i used to have the same problem due to my net connection.. I would be stopped before i began to cast but the server would still think i was moving. what fixed it for me was getting into the habit of turning a little before casting to give my box time to catch up. (not really sure on the exact reason for the problem just guessing, but turning always worked for me...)</P><P>Peace <BR>Kilaelr Darkreaver, 53rd Heretic<BR>Souls of the Ancient<BR>Innoruuk</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
