         I use hot keys to avoid yhis problem. They are set up in this fashion</P><P>Line 1 - /sit on<BR>Line 2 - /sit off<BR>Line 3 - /cast 1</P><P>This same method can be set up to include abilities (great for druid kiting)</P><P>/sit on<BR>/sit off<BR>/doablilty 1 (sense heading for me)<BR>/doability 2 (forage for me)<BR>/cast 1</P><P>I hope this helps!</P><P></P><P>Lady Vyani Shadowheart<BR>Ayonae Ro</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=245891" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=245891</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
